{"tid":351732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"53%香港人支持一地兩檢，教育程度愈低、年紀愈大的受訪者傾向支持方","createTime":"2017-08-08T09:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T04:37:59.000Z","uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"611e9f12b0c57f508c5984a3d909faa00fc533e4","tid":351732,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170808/s00001/1502128187493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170808%2Fs00001%2F1502128187493&d=HV1dzBfdtOGeWDRNYTgTmzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c2773a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170808%2Fs00001%2F1502128187493&h=bd7257bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170808/s00001/1502128187493</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/l0K7zc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fl0K7zc5.jpg&h=3b7d0b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】《明報》委託港大民意研究計劃在8月初做高鐵一地兩檢方案的民意調查，結果顯示52.7%受訪市民支持政府提出的一地兩檢方案，包括在西九龍高鐵站劃出部分地方做「內地口岸區」實施內地法律，在站內完成出入境手續；反對比率為33.9%。有48.2%受訪者認為在一地兩檢安排下，他們對一國兩制的信心不變，表示信心減少的則有34.8%，表示信心增加的有11.4%。<br />\n<br />\n年輕高學歷傾向反對<br />\n<br />\n民調在本月2日至3日以電腦隨機抽樣電話訪問517名18歲或以上香港居民，回應比率為71.6%。根據交叉分析，愈年輕和學歷愈高的受訪者，都傾向反對一地兩檢方案；教育程度愈低、年紀愈大的受訪者傾向支持方案。<br />\n<br />\n對一國兩制增強信心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/o69S1V9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo69S1V9.png&h=e74b6f05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2285395ff0f0a97465c2d9dad62fbf6cc78347ef","tid":351732,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:51:03.000Z","msg":"廢老幾時死"},{"pid":"4749bb4f8b880c1a1e4356400ee7391b53500d13","tid":351732,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾癈老害死下一代"},{"pid":"d8f48c24ea8136dee39f4d41e982643c0342be81","tid":351732,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22764f95749bf209c87678e33c2b51abbe3e8e2","tid":351732,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"點解一定要係香港兩檢？"},{"pid":"079bab038336b5699a8dbc65317e57458050ecd4","tid":351732,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解一定要係香港兩檢？</blockquote><br />\n政治原因吧"},{"pid":"b7e90a26b3de372d31170935e6c4ea672eb21225","tid":351732,"uid":18604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解一定要係香港兩檢？</blockquote><br />\n政治原因吧</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n踩正你頭上畀個下馬威你"}]}